  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bcc\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0bae\u0b95\u0bbe \u0baa\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3 \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb3\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Buddhist Maha Peedhams appeal to party leaders",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Due to the emergence of political instability, there has been a great threat to the security of the country and the lives of the people. Therefore, on this decisive occasion, it is necessary for all the party leaders to unite and establish a proper government, the Buddhist Maha Pedhas have emphasized.",
        "The Buddhist Maha Pedhas, who have requested to refrain from activities including damage to public property during the demonstrations, have asked the people to think and act responsibly.",
        "This has been emphasized in the joint statement issued jointly by the Buddhist Maha Peedhams of Malwattu, Askriya, Amarapura Maha Nikaya and Ramajna Maha Nikaya. The report further states that:",
        "Due to the political instability that has emerged in the country, there is now a great threat to the security of the country and the lives of the people. Without any planning to protect people's lives and solve their problems, the protests will lead to further anarchy in the country.",
        "Thus, on this crucial occasion, we reiterate the need to pay attention to the expectations of the people and under the democratic values, all the party leaders unite and convene the parliament immediately and establish a proper regime so that the reputation of the country in the international community is not affected.",
        "At this critical juncture, as per the law, we should respect the rule of law and express our protest in a peaceful manner.",
        "Instead of that, the protestors should take steps not to engage in any activities including damage to public property. So common people should think and act responsibly.",
        "Also, it is the right of the people to know about the actual situation prevailing in the country. Therefore, we believe that it is the responsibility of the security department to provide space for free information in this regard, protect people's lives and maintain peace in the country."
      ],
